    "feat": {
        "name": "Read Disaster",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "subtype": "feat",
        "text": "You spend 10 minutes and open yourself to the divine mysteries of the world, peering into the most sinister portents of the future. You gain the effects of *augury*, except you learn only about the dangers ahead; any results of \u201cgood\u201d are instead \u201cnothing,\u201d and results of \u201cmixed\u201d are instead \u201cbad.\u201d If you are legendary in Religion, you take only 1 minute to Read Disaster.",
